Rating: 4
incredibly delicious, lowfat (vegen, even)! I served it over coconut sorbet because we are currently not eating dairy. I came across little pieces of orange rind that had been boiled in the syrup...yum! Make this with the spring rhubarb that is probably just coming on now in your garden now. Don't worry about peeling the rhubarb.

